column2: select agn.*, spec.specObjID as SDSS_specObjID, spec.z as SDSS_specz, spec.zErr as SDSS_speczErr, spec.zWarning as SDSS_zWarning, spec.velDisp as SDSS_velDisp, spec.velDispErr as SDSS_velDispErr, spec.bestObjID as SDSS_bestObjID into mydb.StageOne from MyDB.Sabater_AGN as agn, DR7.SpecObjAll as spec where agn.ra between spec.ra-# and spec.ra+#   and agn.dec between spec.dec-# and spec.dec+#   and agn.mjd = spec.mjd   and agn.plate = spec.plate   and agn.fiberid = spec.fiberid
